        <obo:IAO_0000115>This is an AE which is defined in the medical literature as &quot;flatus expelled through the anus&quot; or the &quot;quality or state of being flatulent&quot;, which is defined in turn as &quot;marked by or affected with gases generated in the intestine or stomach; likely to cause digestive flatulence&quot;.</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <obo:IAO_0000117>QY, JX, HY</obo:IAO_0000117>
