        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#ObsoleteClass"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>This is an AE which is a mainstay of adjunctive therapy for superficial bladder cancer that increases length of disease progression-free survival and it usually well tolerated, moderate to severe local and systemic infectious complications can occur with this immunotherapy.</obo:IAO_0000115>
