        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#ObsoleteClass"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>This is an AE which is a common side effect of various medical conditions which manifests as a reduced sense of touch or sensation, or a partial loss of sensitivity to sensory stimuli such as hypoaesthesia facial.</obo:IAO_0000115>
