        <obo:IAO_0000115>This is an AE which is a deviation from normal walking (gait).</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <obo:IAO_0000117>QY, JX, HY</obo:IAO_0000117>
        <obo:IAO_0000119>http://en.volupedia.org/wiki/Gait_abnormality</obo:IAO_0000119>
